description.value: EcoLink is a DAO. We are planting tree with the help of blockchain technology. The climate change rapidly increasing and the co2 also increasing. If we want to live in this earth then we have to plant more trees. Currently we are making a projet of NFT and token to stop climate change. If any one buy a NFT from our DAO he will plant a tree and he also can track his tree with the help of blockchain. Many of our project are coming soon! 1Tree = 1NFT = 4.5ton CA. Lest make a carbon free earth!
